You can see seven top tricks (two Spades, two Hearts, two Diamonds and the @CA) and need two more. There is no chance of an extra trick in Spades or Hearts and little prospect of getting anything out of Clubs so the focus of the deal is on playing the Diamond suit to your advantage. If you can make four tricks here you are home and dry.|
